description:
National Review for iOS is here! America’s most widely read and influential magazine of conservative news and opinion is now available for your iPad and iPhone. Subscribe and enjoy every word and illustration that’s in the print edition as soon as each new issue is released. Browse, download, and enjoy any issue of National Review in its entirety from 2005 to the present. Or search for and purchase any individual magazine article or section dating all the way back to the very first National Review in 1955!

Of course, all of your downloads are stored on the device, available for viewing anywhere and anytime.

How to access National Review on your iPad or iPhone:

● Download the app for free!

● If you are an existing National Review/Digital subscriber, log in via the National Review app to access to all the digitized issues within your subscription period.

● Current non-subscribers can subscribe within the National Review app. Auto-Renewable in-app subscriptions are available at 6 months for $11.99, or 12 months for $19.99. These auto-renewable subscriptions can be turned off at any time via the iTunes account settings on your device.

● Complete issues (from 2005 to present) may be purchased individually for $1.99.

● ANY article or section in the long history of National Review may be purchased for $0.99!

-- SUBSCRIPTIONS AVAILABLE -- 

1 Year Auto-Renew for $19.99 

6 Months Auto-Renew for $11.99 

-- SUBSCRIPTIONS AUTO-RENEW -- 

Subscriptions will process automatically to your Apple iTunes payment method. To cancel your auto-renew subscription please access the iTunes account settings. 
Download the free Gulfshore Life magazine app, then follow the prompts to buy complete issues. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal. Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period. Thank you.

Send any questions, comments, and support requests to appsupport@nationalreview.com. Visit us on the web at www.nationalreview.com.
